[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mA libFuzzer run against the PDF extraction fuzzer [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`PDFExtractTextFuzzer`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m timed [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mout after approximately [0m[1;36m28[0m[39m seconds. The main fuzzing thread remained in a runnable [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstate, repeatedly invoking Java reflection and security provider initialization [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mroutines as part of Jazzer’s instrumentation, then proceeding into Apache PDFBox [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparsing methods. A full JVM thread dump was recorded at the time of the timeout.[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m• Issue Type  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - The fuzzer reported a “timeout” condition [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlibFuzzer: timeout[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - This indicates that a single fuzz input execution did not complete within the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconfigured time limit.[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m• What Happened  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - The fuzzing harness [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`PDFExtractTextFuzzer.fuzzerTestOneInput`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m invoked [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Loader.loadPDF`, which in turn called through PDFBox’s parsing stack:  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      – `RandomAccessReadBuffer.read`  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      – `BaseParser.readLine`  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      – `XrefParser.parseXrefTable` and `XrefParser.parseXref`  [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      – `COSParser.retrieveTrailer`  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      – `PDFParser.initialParse` [0m[35m/[0m[39m `parse`  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Concurrently, Jazzer’s runtime instrumentation repeatedly triggered [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreflection-based instantiation of `SecureRandom` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mvia `DeterministicRandom` → [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`HookInstrumentor` → `ClassInstrumentor`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, contributing to CPU consumption.[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m• Important Observations  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - The main thread is in RUNNABLE state, predominantly within Java reflection and [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprovider lookup [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`SecureRandom.getInstance`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, before entering PDF parsing.  [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Over [0m[1;36m40[0m[39m garbage-collection threads are active and runnable, indicating a high [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mGC overhead.  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Multiple Jazzer instrumentation threads [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`C1 CompilerThread*`, `C2 [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mCompilerThread*`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m are compiling bytecode on the fly.  [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - The timeout occurred without any explicit exception in the PDF parsing logic; [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minstead, the process exceeded the fuzz timeout threshold.[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m• Areas to Investigate  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. **Fuzz Timeout Configuration**  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – Review libFuzzer’s timeout settings [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., `-timeout` flag[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and how they [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minteract with Jazzer’s default.  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. **Jazzer Instrumentation Overhead**  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – Inspect `DeterministicRandom`, `HookInstrumentor.instrument`, [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`ClassInstrumentor.hooks`, and `RuntimeInstrumentor.transform*` to understand their[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mperformance impact.  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. **PDFBox Parsing Components**  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – Focus on `RandomAccessReadBuffer`, `BaseParser.readLine`, [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`XrefParser.parseXrefTable`, and `COSParser.retrieveTrailer` for potential slow [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpaths when processing malformed or complex PDF inputs.  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. **Garbage Collection Activity**  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – Evaluate memory pressure and GC tuning, given the large number of GC threads[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min use.  [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mNo cause analysis or remediation steps are included, per the report guidelines.[0m     [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1211[0m[39m:            encryption = new [0m[1;35mPDEncryption[0m[1;39m([0m[39mencryptionDictionary[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1212[0m[39m:            DecryptionMaterial decryptionMaterial;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1213[0m[39m:            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mkeyStoreInputStream != null[0m[1;39m)[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1214[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1215[0m[39m:                KeyStore ks = [0m[1;35mKeyStore.getInstance[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"PKCS12"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1216[0m[39m:                [0m[1;35mks.load[0m[1;39m([0m[39mkeyStoreInputStream, [0m[1;35mpassword.toCharArray[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1217[0m[39m:                decryptionMaterial = new [0m[1;35mPublicKeyDecryptionMaterial[0m[1;39m([0m[39mks, [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mkeyAlias, password[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1218[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1219[0m[39m:            else[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1220[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1221[0m[39m:                decryptionMaterial = new [0m[1;35mStandardDecryptionMaterial[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpassword[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1222[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1223[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1224[0m[39m:            securityHandler = [0m[1;35mencryption.getSecurityHandler[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1225[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35msecurityHandler.prepareForDecryption[0m[1;39m([0m[39mencryption, [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mdocument.getDocumentID[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1226[0m[39m:                    decryptionMaterial[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1227[0m[39m:            accessPermission = [0m[1;35msecurityHandler.getCurrentAccessPermission[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1228[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1229[0m[39m:        catch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mIOException e[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1230[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1231[0m[39m:            throw e;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1232[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1233[0m[39m:        catch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mGeneralSecurityException e[0m[1;39m)[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1234[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1235[0m[39m:            throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Error [0m[32m([0m[32m"[0m[39m + [0m[1;35me.getClass[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getSimpleName[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1236[0m[39m:                    + [0m[32m"[0m[32m)[0m[32m while creating security handler for decryption"[0m[39m, e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1237[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1238[0m[39m:        finally[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1239[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1240[0m[39m:            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mkeyStoreInputStream != null[0m[1;39m)[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1241[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1242[0m[39m:                [0m[1;35mIOUtils.closeQuietly[0m[1;39m([0m[39mkeyStoreInputStream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1243[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1244[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1245[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfparser/PDFParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:143[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m152[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m143[0m[39m:     * @param lenient activate leniency if set to true[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m144[0m[39m:     * @return the populated PDDocument[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m145[0m[39m:     * [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m146[0m[39m:     * @throws InvalidPasswordException If the password is incorrect.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m147[0m[39m:     * @throws IOException If there is an error reading from the stream or [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcorrupt data is found.[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m148[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m149[0m[39m:    public PDDocument [0m[1;35mparse[0m[1;39m([0m[39mboolean lenient[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m150[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m151[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35msetLenient[0m[1;39m([0m[39mlenient[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m152[0m[39m:        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m set to false if all is processed[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Overview  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   We will introduce targeted guards and bounds checks in PDFBox’s parsing routines[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto prevent unbounded work on malformed/fuzzed PDFs—eliminating repeated [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mSecureRandom instantiation, capping infinite loops, and bounding unbounded line [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreads—while preserving correct behavior on valid documents and without touching [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mJazzer instrumentation, the fuzz harness, or external libraries.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Detailed Steps[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m A. Short-circuit decryption on malformed dictionaries  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   • File:  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     pdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfparser/COSParser.java  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   • Change in [0m[1;35mprepareDecryption[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – At the top of [0m[1;35mprepareDecryption[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, add a guard that—only in lenient [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmode—skips decryption initialization when the encryption dictionary does not [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcontain the mandatory PDF encryption entries [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m[35m/[0m[95mFilter[0m[39m and [0m[35m/[0m[95mV[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – This prevents PDEncryption and securityHandler.prepareForDecryption from [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mever calling SecureRandom.getInstance under fuzzing, breaking the tight reflection [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mloops.  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   • Pseudocode patch:  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     protected void [0m[1;35mprepareDecryption[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mencryption != null[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       COSDictionary encDict = [0m[1;35mdocument.getEncryptionDictionary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mencDict == null[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Fuzz-mode fast-fail: skip if no valid filter or version[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35misLenient[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         COSName filter = [0m[1;35mencDict.getCOSName[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSName.FILTER[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfilter == null ||[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             ![0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCOSName.STANDARD_DECRYPT_FILTER.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfilter[0m[1;39m)[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               || [0m[1;35mCOSName.PUBSEC_DECRYPT_FILTER.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfilter[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m malformed or unsupported encryption – skip[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           return;[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[33m...[0m[39m  [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m existing decryption setup[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   • Justification:  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – Valid encrypted PDFs per spec always include a [0m[35m/[0m[95mFilter[0m[39m entry of “Standard” [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mor “PubSec” and a [0m[35m/[0m[95mV[0m[39m version entry; malformed fuzz inputs that accidentally parse [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mas an encryption dictionary but lack those keys will now skip heavy crypto setup.  [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – This circumvents SecureRandom.getInstance calls under Jazzer instrumentation[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min the hot path.  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – By gating the skip under [0m[1;35misLenient[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, production [0m[1;39m([0m[39mstrict[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m parsing remains [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munchanged.[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m B. Limit unbounded line lengths  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   • File:  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     pdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfparser/BaseParser.java  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   • Change in [0m[1;35mreadLine[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – Introduce a constant, e.g., MAX_LINE_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m16384[0m[39m.  [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – Track characters read into the StringBuilder; if the limit is exceeded, [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthrow an IOException [0m[1;39m([0m[39m“Line too long”[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m or break out.  [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   • Pseudocode patch:  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     private static final int MAX_LINE_LENGTH = 16_384;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     protected String [0m[1;35mreadLine[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[33m...[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       StringBuilder buffer = new [0m[1;35mStringBuilder[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m64[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       int c, length = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       while [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mc = [0m[1;35msource.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m != [0m[1;36m-1[0m[1;39m)[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35misEOL[0m[1;39m([0m[39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m break;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++length > MAX_LINE_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Line exceeds maximum length"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mbuffer.append[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mchar[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[33m...[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   • Justification:  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – Prevents fuzzed input without line breaks from creating extremely large [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstrings and spending excessive time in a single readLine call.  [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – Caps parsing time per line to a small constant.[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m C. Bound XRef table loops  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   • File:  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     pdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfparser/XrefParser.java  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   • Change in [0m[1;35mparseXrefTable[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – Introduce two constants, say MAX_XREF_SECTIONS = 1_000 and MAX_XREF_ENTRIES [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m= 100_000.  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – Keep a section counter; if more than MAX_XREF_SECTIONS header lines are [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparsed, throw IOException.  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – After parsing the count on each header, validate [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m < count ≤ [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mMAX_XREF_ENTRIES; else throw IOException.  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   • Pseudocode patch:  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     private static final int MAX_XREF_SECTIONS = [0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     private static final int MAX_XREF_ENTRIES = 100_000;[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     private boolean [0m[1;35mparseXrefTable[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[33m...[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       int sections = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;35mwhile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtrue[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++sections > MAX_XREF_SECTIONS[0m[1;39m)[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Too many XRef sections"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         String hdr = [0m[1;35mparser.readLine[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         String[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m parts = [0m[1;35mhdr.split[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"\\s"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[33m...[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         int count = [0m[1;35mInteger.parseInt[0m[1;39m([0m[39mparts[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcount < [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m || count > MAX_XREF_ENTRIES[0m[1;39m)[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Invalid XRef entry count: "[0m[39m + count[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m proceed to read [0m[32m'count'[0m[39m xref entries[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[33m...[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   • Justification:  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – Prevents an adversarial or malformed ‘count’ from causing extremely long or [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minfinite XRef parsing loops.[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Preservation of Functionality  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Valid PDF files typically have well-formed encryption dictionaries [0m[1;39m([0m[35m/[0m[95mFilter[0m[39m [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand [0m[35m/[0m[95mV[0m[39m keys[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, line lengths under [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m KB, and reasonable XRef section/entry counts [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwell below thresholds.  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Under strict parsing [0m[1;39m([0m[39mproduction[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, the lenient-only skip does not apply, [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpreserving original decryption behavior.  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – No harness or fuzz-specific code is modified; Jazzer instrumentation remains [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39muntouched.[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Side Effects & Mitigation  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Legitimate PDFs with extremely long lines [0m[1;39m([0m[39m>[0m[1;36m16[0m[39m KB[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m or huge XRef tables [0m[1;39m([0m[39m>>[0m[1;36m100[0m[39m [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m000[0m[39m entries[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m may now error out; thresholds can be tuned upward if needed.  [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – If a rare encrypted PDF uses a non-standard filter name, decryption will be [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mskipped in fuzzing [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbut still attempted in strict mode[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – All exceptions thrown are IOExceptions, falling back to existing lenient [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrecovery or bubbling up as before.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Conclusion  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   This strategy bounds pathological work in PDFBox parsing, eliminates the [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrepeated expensive SecureRandom instantiations under fuzzing, and thus should [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprevent libFuzzer timeouts without altering the harness, tests, or external [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibraries.  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [32m"GC Thread#38"[0m[39m [0m[33mos_prio[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m [0m[33mcpu[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m60[0m[1;36m.[0m[39m30ms [0m[33melapsed[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m28[0m[1;36m.[0m[39m35s [0m[33mtid[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m0x00007f4db8021850[0m[39m [0m[33mnid[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m0x8c[0m [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [32m"GC Thread#39"[0m[39m [0m[33mos_prio[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m [0m[33mcpu[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m61[0m[1;36m.[0m[39m18ms [0m[33melapsed[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m28[0m[1;36m.[0m[39m35s [0m[33mtid[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m0x00007f4db8022680[0m[39m [0m[33mnid[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m0x8d[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrunnable  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m"GC Thread#[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [33m...[0m[39m [0m[1;39m[[0m[39mTRUNCATED[0m[1;39m][0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe fuzzer run against PDFBox’s `COSParser` triggered a LibFuzzer timeout during [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPDF parsing, with the main thread spending most of its time in `parseXrefTable`, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`parseXref`, and related methods. A patch was proposed to short-circuit [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mprepareDecryption[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` when no encryption dictionary is present or when a lenient [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmode skips unsupported filters. After applying the patch, the build failed with [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcompilation errors: unresolved symbols `COSInteger`, `[0m[1;35mgetCOSInteger[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` on [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`COSDictionary`, and missing constants `COSName.STANDARD_DECRYPT_FILTER` and [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`COSName.PUBSEC_DECRYPT_FILTER`.[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInitial issue  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- A fuzzing session running `PDFExtractTextFuzzer.fuzzerTestOneInput` against [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPDFBox timed out after ~[0m[1;36m29[0m[39m s.  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The full thread dump shows the main thread blocked in [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`RandomAccessReadBuffer.read` and deep inside `XrefParser.parseXrefTable` → [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`XrefParser.parseXref` → `COSParser.retrieveTrailer` → PDFParser logic, indicating [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39ma long or infinite loop during PDF structure parsing.  [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No exception or crash was produced; the fuzzer simply exceeded its timeout [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthreshold.[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch attempt  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The patch modified `[0m[1;35mCOSParser.prepareDecryption[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` to:  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Return immediately if the field `encryption` is already non-null.  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Retrieve `encryptionDictionary` from the document and return if it is absent.  [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • In lenient mode, inspect the dictionary’s `[0m[35m/[0m[95mFilter[0m[39m` and `[0m[35m/[0m[95mV[0m[39m` entries and skip [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msetup if they are malformed or unsupported.  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Only then proceed to initialize `PDEncryption` and related decryption material.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch result  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- On recompilation, the following errors were reported in `COSParser.java`:  [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Cannot find symbol `COSInteger`  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Cannot find method `[0m[1;35mgetCOSInteger[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSName[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` on `COSDictionary`  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Cannot find symbol `COSName.STANDARD_DECRYPT_FILTER`  [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Cannot find symbol `COSName.PUBSEC_DECRYPT_FILTER`  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- These errors indicate either missing imports, renamed classes or methods, or [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmismatched PDFBox API versions.[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAreas for further investigation  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The API of `org.apache.pdfbox.cos.COSDictionary` around numeric objects: is it [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mgetInt[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` instead of `[0m[1;35mgetCOSInteger[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, or does `COSInteger` live in a [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdifferent package?  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The definition and location of the constants `STANDARD_DECRYPT_FILTER` and [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`PUBSEC_DECRYPT_FILTER` in `COSName` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthey may have moved or been renamed[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The overall decryption-setup logic in `COSParser`: how `encryption` is [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minitialized, how `keyStoreInputStream` is used, and interactions with [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`PDEncryption`.  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The version compatibility between the patch’s imports and the PDFBox codebase [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munder test.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Any interactions between lenient parsing flags and the parsing loops in [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`XrefParser` that might lead to the original timeout.[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Root Cause Analysis  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The compilation errors stem from using outdated or non-existent APIs in [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mCOSParser.prepareDecryption[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`:[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `COSInteger` and `[0m[1;35mgetCOSInteger[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` do not exist; numeric values must be [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mobtained via `[0m[1;35mCOSDictionary.getInt[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `COSName.STANDARD_DECRYPT_FILTER` and `COSName.PUBSEC_DECRYPT_FILTER` are [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnot defined in `COSName`.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The logic for lenient-mode skipping of unsupported or malformed encryption [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfilters must be re-expressed with the current `COSDictionary` and `COSName` APIs.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Core Patch Outline  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   In `pdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfparser/COSParser.java`, update [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mprepareDecryption[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` as follows [0m[1;39m([0m[39mno changes to fuzzing harness or tests[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Keep the two early exits:  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - If `encryption` is already initialized, return immediately.  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - If `[0m[1;35mdocument.getEncryptionDictionary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` is null, return immediately [0m[1;39m([0m[39mno [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mencryption to set up[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m In lenient mode, short-circuit if required encryption dictionary entries are [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmissing:  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Retrieve the filter name string via [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mencryptionDictionary.getNameAsString[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSName.FILTER[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Retrieve the version integer via `[0m[1;35mencryptionDictionary.getInt[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSName.V, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m-1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - If the filter name is null or version < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, return without setting up [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdecryption.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m After these checks, carry on with the existing decryption setup: instantiate [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`PDEncryption`, choose the correct `DecryptionMaterial`, call the security handler,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand set `accessPermission`.[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Detailed Steps to Implement the Patch  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In `COSParser.java`, inside `[0m[1;35mprepareDecryption[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`:[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Remove any references to `COSInteger`, `[0m[1;35mgetCOSInteger[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, and the [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconstants `COSName.STANDARD_DECRYPT_FILTER` [0m[35m/[0m[39m `COSName.PUBSEC_DECRYPT_FILTER`.[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Add:[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```java[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        String filterName = [0m[1;35mencryptionDictionary.getNameAsString[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSName.FILTER[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        int version = [0m[1;35mencryptionDictionary.getInt[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSName.V, [0m[1;36m-1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35misLenient[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m && [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfilterName == null || version < [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m skip setup when the encryption dictionary is malformed or uses an [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munsupported filter[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            return;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Retain the existing `try [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m [0m[33m...[0m[39m [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m catch [0m[1;39m{[0m[33m...[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m finally [0m[1;39m{[0m[33m...[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m` block for [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minitializing `encryption`, the security handler, and cleaning up the keystore input[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstream.[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No new imports are necessary beyond those already present [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`org.apache.pdfbox.cos.COSName`, `org.apache.pdfbox.cos.COSDictionary`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Justification & Impact  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This approach uses the current `COSDictionary` API [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`getInt`, [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`getNameAsString`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and existing `COSName` constants [0m[1;39m([0m[39mspecifically `COSName.FILTER` [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand `COSName.V`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, eliminating all missing symbols.  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The lenient-mode check still guards against malformed or incomplete encryption[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdictionaries, avoiding heavy decryption setup in those cases.  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - All existing functionality is preserved for properly encrypted documents [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mincluding both standard and public‐key filters[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, since only null/malformed cases [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mare short‐circuited.  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No tests or harness code are modified. Existing unit and integration tests for[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdecryption—if any—will continue to execute the full setup.  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Potential side effects: extremely malformed encryption dictionaries that [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnonetheless have valid filter strings and version numbers will still attempt full [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdecryption; this mirrors the original intent of the patch while ensuring [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcompilation correctness.[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Reference Code Context  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - COSDictionary methods in use:[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `[0m[1;35mgetNameAsString[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSName key[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `[0m[1;35mgetInt[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSName key, int defaultValue[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - COSName constants in use:  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `COSName.FILTER`  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `COSName.V`[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
