[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mA Jazzer-based fuzz run against Apache PDFBox timed out [0m[1;39m([0m[39m~[0m[1;36m28[0m[39m – [0m[1;36m29[0m[39m s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m while parsing [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPDF inputs. The initial thread dump showed the main fuzz thread stuck in the [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minstrumentation startup and then inside PDFBox’s parsing routines [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnotably [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`BaseParser.readLine` during `XrefParser.parseXrefTable`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. A patch was applied to [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`COSParser` to short-circuit encryption setup in lenient mode—skipping `new [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mPDEncryption[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` when the encryption dictionary is malformed or unsupported. [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mDespite this change, the fuzzer still times out in essentially the same parsing [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcode paths [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`BaseParser.readLine` → `XrefParser.parseXrefTable` → [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`COSParser.retrieveTrailer` → `PDFParser.parse`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Initial Issue  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- A libFuzzer run [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`ERROR: libFuzzer: timeout`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m halted after approximately [0m[1;36m28.9[0m[39m s. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The main thread was RUNNABLE with a deep stack trace that started in Jazzer’s [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdeterministic-random hook and quickly descended into PDFBox parsing:  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • `TraceDataFlowNativeCallbacks.traceCmpInt`  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • `BaseParser.readLine`  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • `XrefParser.parseXrefTable` → `XrefParser.parseXref`  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • `COSParser.retrieveTrailer`  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • `PDFParser.initialParse` → `PDFParser.parse`  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • `Loader.loadPDF`  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • user fuzz entry point `PDFExtractTextFuzzer.fuzzerTestOneInput`  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mImportant observations:  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The fuzzer did not crash but hung—indicating a possible infinite loop or [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mextremely slow processing in the cross-reference/trailer parsing.  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The hang occurs during low-level line reading [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`BaseParser.readLine`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and XRef [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtable parsing.  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Patch Attempt  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mLocation: `COSParser.java` around the encryption-initialization block [0m[1;39m([0m[39moriginal [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlines ≈ [0m[1;36m1205[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch snippet:[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```diff[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m before: unguarded PDEncryption setup[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-    try[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-        encryption = new [0m[1;35mPDEncryption[0m[1;39m([0m[39mencryptionDictionary[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35misLenient[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+        String filterName = [0m[1;35mencryptionDictionary.getNameAsString[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSName.FILTER[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+        int version = [0m[1;35mencryptionDictionary.getInt[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSName.V, [0m[1;36m-1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m malformed or unsupported encryption – skip heavy setup in lenient mode[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfilterName == null || version < [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            return;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    try[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+        encryption = new [0m[1;35mPDEncryption[0m[1;39m([0m[39mencryptionDictionary[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis adds an early return in lenient mode when the encryption dictionary lacks a [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfilter name or a valid version, avoiding the `PDEncryption` constructor’s “heavy [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msetup.”[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Resulting Behavior  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- After rebuilding with this patch, the fuzzer still reports `ERROR: libFuzzer: [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtimeout` [0m[1;39m([0m[39m~[0m[1;36m27.9[0m[39m s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The second thread dump again shows the main thread stuck in the same parsing [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mregion, now without the initial instrumentation-bootstrap frames but still in:  [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • `TraceDataFlowNativeCallbacks.traceCmpInt`  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • `BaseParser.readLine`  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • `XrefParser.parseXrefTable` → `COSParser.retrieveTrailer`  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • `PDFParser.parse` → `Loader.loadPDF` → [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`PDFExtractTextFuzzer.fuzzerTestOneInput`  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mNo reduction in execution time or avoidance of the looping parse logic was [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mobserved.[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Areas for Further Investigation  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTo understand and address the timeout, the following components should be reviewed:[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **BaseParser.readLine**  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Check loop termination, buffering logic, and handling of malformed line [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mendings.  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **XrefParser.parseXrefTable [0m[35m/[0m[39m parseXref**  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Inspect state transitions and exit conditions when encountering unexpected [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdata.  [0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **COSParser.retrieveTrailer**  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Evaluate how trailer retrieval loops over possible [0m[32m"startxref"[0m[39m locations, [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mespecially in lenient mode.  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **PDFParser.initialParse**  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Review the overall parsing flow and how it hands off between header, body, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mxref, trailer, and encryption.  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mA holistic view of these interactions will help identify why certain malformed or [0m  [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m100[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m101[0m[39m:    private static final char[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m EOF_MARKER = [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m [0m[32m'%'[0m[39m, [0m[32m'%'[0m[39m, [0m[32m'E'[0m[39m, [0m[32m'O'[0m[39m, [0m[32m'F'[0m[39m [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m;[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m102[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m103[0m[39m:     * obj-marker.[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m104[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m105[0m[39m:    private static final char[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m OBJ_MARKER = [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m [0m[32m'o'[0m[39m, [0m[32m'b'[0m[39m, [0m[32m'j'[0m[39m [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m;[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m106[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m107[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m108[0m[39m:     * file length.[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m109[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m110[0m[39m:    private final long fileLen;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m111[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m112[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m113[0m[39m:     * is parser using auto healing capacity ?[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m114[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Introduce line-length bounding in BaseParser.readLine to prevent unbounded loops[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mon inputs without EOL:[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Define a new constant `MAX_LINE_LENGTH` [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m [0m[1;36m000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In the readLine loop, track the number of characters read. If the count [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexceeds `MAX_LINE_LENGTH`, throw an `IOException` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor break[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to abort parsing of [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat line.[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This turnstiles extremely long or delimiter-free data into a controlled [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfailure, allowing the fuzzer to move on instead of hanging.[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Add sanity caps in XrefParser.parseXrefTable to bound nested loops:[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Section count limit:[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Introduce `MAX_XREF_SECTIONS` [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m[1;36m50[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Before entering the `while [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtrue[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` for reading xref sections, initialize a [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msection counter.[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - On each iteration, increment the counter; if it exceeds [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`MAX_XREF_SECTIONS`, log a warning and return `false`.[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Entry-count limit:[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - After parsing the section header `count`, validate `count` against [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`MAX_XREF_ENTRIES` [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m[1;36m50[0m[39m [0m[1;36m000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. If out of range, log and return `false`.[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - This prevents a single section from driving an enormous inner loop.[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Aggregate-entry limit [0m[1;39m([0m[39moptional[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Maintain a running total of entries processed. If the total exceeds a [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhigh-water mark, bail early.[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Cap chained-xref parsing in XrefParser.parseXref:[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Introduce `MAX_CHAINED_XREF` [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m[1;36m10[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In the `while [0m[1;39m([0m[39mprev > [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m && prev != lastPrev[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` loop, track iterations. If the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mloop count exceeds `MAX_CHAINED_XREF`, throw an `IOException` to abort.[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This prevents adversarial PDFs from chaining dozens of xref tables through [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[35m/[0m[95mPrev[0m[39m` entries.[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Ensure these guards apply in lenient mode [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwhere most fallback loops occur[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. In [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstrict mode, existing exceptions already abort early.[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Preserve existing functionality for well-formed PDFs:[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Choose thresholds large enough to accommodate realistic file structures [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g.,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlines rarely exceed [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m [0m[1;36m000[0m[39m chars; sections rarely exceed dozens[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Wrap new checks under `[0m[1;35misLenient[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` where appropriate, so strict parsing [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbehaves unchanged for normative inputs.[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Do not modify harness or fuzzing logic. All changes occur within BaseParser, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mXrefParser, and COSParser classes.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mExplanation:[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The hang originates in unbounded `[0m[1;35mreadLine[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` calls [0m[1;39m([0m[39mno EOL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, compounded by loops[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min `parseXrefTable` reading many sections or entries and chained xref handling. [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- By bounding line length and loop iterations, malformed or adversarial inputs will[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcause controlled `IOException`s, gracefully aborting parsing rather than spinning [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindefinitely.[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This solution preserves the core parsing flow: well-formed PDFs remain [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munaffected; malformations lead to early failure. [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Similar “circuit-breaker” patterns already exist [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., `lastPrev` check for [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[35m/[0m[95mPrev[0m[39m` loops[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m; these new thresholds complement them to prevent runtime blow-ups.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Side effects: extremely large but valid PDFs that exceed these thresholds will [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39merror out; however, thresholds are set high enough to avoid false positives in [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreal-world documents. If necessary, thresholds can be exposed via system properties[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfor fine-tuning.[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
